@startuml
' === Impostazioni per A4 Verticale ===
scale max 1024 width
page 1x2
skinparam pageMargin 10
skinparam dpi 300

' Sviluppo rigorosamente verticale
top to bottom direction
skinparam classAttributeIconSize 0
skinparam nodesep 40
skinparam ranksep 70
skinparam classAttributeIconSize 0
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam linetype ortho
skinparam ArrowThickness 2
skinparam ArrowColor #1F2937
skinparam ArrowFontColor #111827
skinparam ArrowFontSize 10
skinparam ArrowFontStyle bold
skinparam defaultTextAlignment left
skinparam wrapWidth 220
skinparam maxMessageSize 80
skinparam handwritten false
skinparam packageStyle rectangle
allowmixing

' ==========================================
' LIVELLO 2: DUMB COMPONENTS (Presentational)
' ==========================================
class ProcessMetadataComponent << Dumb >> {
  + data: input<ProcessDetail>
}
class DocumentIndexComponent << Dumb >>



' ==========================================
' LIVELLO 3: CONTRATTI E SERVICES (Facade)
' ==========================================
interface IProcessFacade << Contract >> {
  + getState(): Signal<ProcessState>
  + loadProcess(id: string): Promise<void>
  + isProcess(id: string): Promise<boolean>
}

class ProcessFacade implements IProcessFacade {
  - ipcGateway: IIpcGateway
  - cache: IpcCacheService
  - state: signal<ProcessState>
  + getState(): Signal<ProcessState>
  + loadProcess(id: string): Promise<void>
  + isProcess(id: string): Promise<boolean>
}


' ==========================================
' LIVELLO MAPPING (Trasformazione Dati)
' ==========================================
class Mapper << Mapper >> {
  + mapProcessDtoToDetail(rawData: any): ProcessDetail
}

class ProcessDTO << DTO >> {
  + id: number
  + metadata: any
  << IPC Payload >>
}

class DocumentClassDTO << DTO >> {
  + id: number
  + name: string
  + uuid: string
}

' Il Facade preleva i DTO (tramite vari fetch)
ProcessFacade ..> Mapper : uses
ProcessFacade ..> ProcessDTO : fetches via IPC
ProcessFacade ..> DocumentClassDTO : fetches via IPC
Mapper ..> ProcessDTO : takes
Mapper ..> ProcessDetail : creates

' ==========================================
' LIVELLO 4: DOMAIN MODELS E STATO MAPPATO
' ==========================================
class ProcessState << State >> {
  + detail: ProcessDetail | null
  + loading: boolean
  + error: AppError | null
}

class ProcessDetail << Model >> {
  + processId: string
  + processUuid: string
  + integrityStatus: string
}

note bottom of ProcessDetail
  <b>Sottomodelli omessi/compressi:</b>
  * ProcessCoreMetadata: 1
  * ProcessOverviewData: 1
  * ProcessSubmissionData: 1
  * ProcessConservationData: 1
  * ProcessDocumentClassInfo: 1
  * ProcessCustomMetadataEntry: 0..*
  * DocumentIndexEntryDTO: 0..*
end note

class ProcessCoreMetadata << Data >>
class ProcessOverviewData << Data >>
class ProcessConservationData << Data >>
class DocumentIndexEntryDTO << Data >>

' Mapping Strutturale dello Stato
ProcessFacade --> ProcessState : manages via signal
ProcessState -->  ProcessDetail : contains

' Associazione Modello Composito
ProcessDetail  -down-> ProcessCoreMetadata
ProcessDetail  -down->  ProcessOverviewData
ProcessDetail  -right->  ProcessConservationData
ProcessDetail  -left->  DocumentIndexEntryDTO

' Vincoli Formativi (Visualizzazione)
ProcessMetadataComponent .up.> ProcessCoreMetadata : displays block
ProcessMetadataComponent .up.> ProcessOverviewData : displays block
ProcessMetadataComponent .up.> ProcessConservationData : displays block
DocumentIndexComponent .left.> DocumentIndexEntryDTO : displays

@enduml